<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.1.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" integrity="sha384-1BmE4kWBq78iYhFldvKuhfTAU6auU8tT94WrHftjDbrCEXSU1oBoqyl2QvZ6jIW3" crossorigin="anonymous">
    <title>Apply Graduation</title>
</head>
<body>
    <a href="/myAcademics"> Back To Academic Record</a>
    <br>
    <p>The requirement courses for graduation are: </p>
    <table>
        <tr>
            <th> <%=required_courses[0]%></th>
            <th> <%=required_courses[1]%></th>
            <th> <%=required_courses[2]%></th>
            <th> <%=required_courses[3]%></th>
        </tr>
        <tr>
